aces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家開始全民投入宣傳工作<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各區連儂牆、airdrop、派街招、擺街站<br />\nfacebook instagram瘋狂轉貼文宣</span></span></strong><br />\n文宣source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0TbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=48b00df7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0TbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=8b86d7cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n8月15日：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）<br />\n8月16日：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n8月17日：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n8月17日：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月18日：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></span></strong><br />\n8月24日：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）<br />\n8月25日：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）<br />\n各位手足，到時見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a26ac051fd97bd1ba62d28e287c0050f8f6ebd9","tid":1469312,"uid":94001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"愈打壓愈要做"},{"pid":"1c5cbb7b70702f8e8be836848aac627046e782f6","tid":1469312,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n永不幫襯"},{"pid":"18a24bf4f262d509aa1bf6b80c39368a84445ef0","tid":1469312,"uid":161209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:53:28.000Z","msg":"［有圖］荃灣手足比人斬到開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471792</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"541dba1bb859f4d3dc54d8d368120bf1b9a80b7c","tid":1469312,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a61a67834598dac8b64dd9d057317ff22019a8a6","tid":1469312,"uid":229733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:56:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed18f95e9fa6db3ad89c0ccfe0963041d08fc47d","tid":1469312,"uid":307000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"76c5d5c43bb7c6218bb52431a77ea6fc26a5c5a1","tid":1469312,"uid":59562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"大大力同我推"},{"pid":"91324edeb8c165cea09ffa5ddb687c9a123e9f98","tid":1469312,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7fe49eecd19ed159faac19d2f40ed0d82cf32a","tid":1469312,"uid":307000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c5d5c43bb7c6218bb52431a77ea6fc26a5c5a1","tid":1469312,"uid":59562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"大大力同我推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"屌 原來佢連牌都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[養心殿2.0] 奶共Kkday無牌經營旅行社業務<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474865</a>"},{"pid":"878f3f47846562b9096d4f89daeedef826b0c40e","tid":1469312,"uid":3039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"即刻del撚左個app佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 